onPostMessage(java.lang.String, android..Description: Called when a tab controlled by this @B_android#support#customtabs#CustomTabsSession_E@ has sent a postMessage. If postMessage() is called from a single thread, then the messages will be posted in the same order. When received on the client side, it is the client's responsibility to preserve the ordering further.

ClassDesc: A callback class for custom tabs client to get messages regarding events in their custom tabs. In the implementation, all callbacks are sent to the UI thread for the client.
